{"tid":960266,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以6000元買華仔個唱門票 買家指黃牛「失蹤」？","createTime":"2018-12-29T09:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T10:02:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"efa6a01dc7eaa7e81c87e219f10f960000c54e48","tid":960266,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20181229/s00009/b324be80c4cdcd6144ccd12bcd0b224d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20181229%2Fs00009%2Fb324be80c4cdcd6144ccd12bcd0b224d.jpg&h=96fda6c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉德華昨晚因喉嚨發炎，在台上忍痛流淚，宣布取消昨晚個唱，他在台上向觀眾鞠躬致歉，而今晚和明晚的個唱亦告取消，華仔要爭取時間休養。<br />\n<br />\n有觀眾在網上留言，聲稱自己以6000元買了官方訂價的980元門票，不過昨晚演唱會被腰斬，這名觀眾獲退款980元，但卻聯絡不了黃牛賣家，遂向演唱會門票買賣群組求助，惹起熱話：「$6000買咗今晚華仔$980演唱會飛，依家退得$980，賣家又失埋蹤，可否報警？」網民旋即議論紛紛，有網民指事件其實與賣家無關，因為雙方已完成交易，不能向賣家追討；亦有網民指買黃牛票有一定風險，購買前必須考慮清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1546059573330&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1546059573330%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181229&d=K8PvC2QKr1Z73RSyGz68H4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=f6fb9293\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1546059573330%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181229&h=adf9bfe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1546059573330&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181229</a>"},{"pid":"d20b24cc12f37772552f0b44a44eb121a8f82f40","tid":960266,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"犯法野去報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c235848d08516bc8972c48216c5aa3bc49b05d3a","tid":960266,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴"},{"pid":"9911ffa38a0b